OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FLottery firm tops list of  
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25FIndia's political donors   
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, A lottery company has topped a list of 
OL,6, India's leading political donors.      
OL,8,FDonations were made under an electoral 
OL,9,Fbonds scheme that allowed anonymity for
OL,10,Fpeople and companies.                  
OL,12,FFuture Gaming and Hotel Services       
OL,13,Femerged as the largest donor, acquiring
OL,14,Fbonds worth at 13bn rupees ($156.7m,   
OL,15,F#123m) from April 2019 to January 2024.
OL,17,FThe ruling Bharatiya Janata Party (BJP)
OL,18,Fwas the biggest beneficiary, securing  
OL,19,Falmost half of the bonds worth 120bn   
OL,20,Frupees donated between 2018 and 2024.  
